rows.label: tlk70000005_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Laura-san! You looked really cool at
the award ceremony!

rows.label: tlk70000005_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought it was a real special event, so
I got my dad to take care of the inn on
his own so I could go.

rows.label: tlk70000005_03_msg0003
rows.name: I was still a bit late for it, though...

rows.label: tlk70000005_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I was trying to figure out what to wear,
and Joey was like, "hurry up!" and
"what's the big deal?"...

rows.label: tlk70000005_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Like, doesn't he understand that you
can't just roll up to a formal event in
regular clothes?

rows.label: tlk70000005_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I was just trying to show a bit of
respect for the occasion. But he doesn't
get it. Idiot...
